## 08 â€” Expected Effects (Qualitative)  

1. **Significant drop in enemy BVR hit probability**;  
2. Enemy AEW&C and radar nets must allocate **more resources just to maintain track**;  
3. **Survivability of limited island fighters increases sharply**;  
4. Provides a **non-symmetric cost-exchange**: small-state pressure against major power air dominance;  
5. Deepens the islandâ€™s overall **A2/AD (Anti-Access / Area Denial)** system.  

